this hormone has a comforting effect. When something is comforting, it makes you feel better.

49
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:52,719
It calms your emotions. Let's listen again.

50
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:57,200
One of the things that we were interested in is what's the difference between people who

51
