So, the thought was that perhaps what's going on is that the people who are enjoying listening to sad music

59
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:42,000
are receiving some sort of excess of prolactin, and people who are listening to sad music,

60
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:46,159
and they just find it incredibly sad and unhelpful, and they don't want to listen to it.

61
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:49,599
Maybe they're not getting enough prolactin when they listen to the music.

62
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:55,439
So, what's happening? Or as Professor Huron said, what's going on?

63
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:59,680
Well, it seems quite simple, though. I'm sure it's very complicated.

64
