People who like sad music are maybe getting too much prolactin, or more than is normal.

65
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:11,280
He describes this as an excess of prolactin, and maybe people who don't like sad music aren't

66
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:17,680
getting enough. So, the idea is that prolactin is a hormone which we find comforting.

67
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:22,319
If our body's released it when we hear sad music, it gives us a good feeling.

68
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:28,399
